{"id":621334,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2019/11/【众人推】new-xisland/","date":"2019-11-02T10:25:37Z","modified":"2019-11-02T10:28:28Z","title":"【众人推】New Xi&#8217;sLand","content":"<p>11月2日，新西兰街头，两名身着中国人民解放军陆、空军军服，持中国国旗，行正步走的“中国军人”出现在香港人抗议示威现场，引起推特网友热议。有网友推断，这应该是两位进行现场cos的“小粉红”，但他们是如何获得军装？有网友质疑，如果两名持美国国旗穿美国军服的人出现在中国街头会怎样？有网友忧虑，像新西兰、澳洲这样的国家，应该更警惕红色力量的渗透。</p>\n<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-width=\"550\" data-dnt=\"true\">\n<p lang=\"zh\" dir=\"ltr\">新西兰的小粉红跟被下了药似的，有没有一种朝鲜人出国了的即视感？你们哪里被渗透的咋样？ <a href=\"https://t.co/GnDQh0Wgse\">pic.twitter.com/GnDQh0Wgse</a></p>\n<p>&mdash; 叫啥不吃饭 (@7opk8wu2GokafWl) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/7opk8wu2GokafWl/status/1190450588342865922?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">November 2, 2019</a></p></blockquote>\n<p><script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script></p>\n<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-width=\"550\" data-dnt=\"true\">\n<p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">1. this happened in New Zealand<br />2. this did not happen because of <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/halloween2019?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#halloween2019</a> <br />PM <a href=\"https://twitter.com/jacindaardern?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@jacindaardern</a>，why would ur country allow Chinese Amy marching on street &amp; intimatng others people supporting HongKong‘s protest<a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/StandWithHongKong?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#StandWithHongKong</a><a href=\"https://t.co/IKtQ2H2IsO\">pic.twitter.com/IKtQ2H2IsO</a></p>\n<p>&mdash; 巴丢草  Badiucao (@badiucao) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/badiucao/status/1190496734331334656?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">November 2, 2019</a></p></blockquote>\n<p><script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script></p>\n<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-width=\"550\" data-dnt=\"true\">\n<p lang=\"zh\" dir=\"ltr\">这两个cosplay 制服上带了军衔 如果不是现役，涉嫌冒充中国人民解放军。 <a href=\"https://t.co/UjIQ0nwuL3\">https://t.co/UjIQ0nwuL3</a></p>\n<p>&mdash; Wu Lebao🇦🇺 (@MerlotN) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/MerlotN/status/1190494865664049155?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">November 2, 2019</a></p></blockquote>\n<p><script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script></p>\n<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-width=\"550\" data-dnt=\"true\">\n<p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">New Xi&#39;sland 😉</p>\n<p>&mdash; JetStream (@JetStre88984665) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/JetStre88984665/status/1190564064105099268?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">November 2, 2019</a></p></blockquote>\n<p><script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script></p>\n<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-width=\"550\" data-dnt=\"true\">\n<p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">True quality of the protesters. <a href=\"https://t.co/TOH3QoFrYI\">pic.twitter.com/TOH3QoFrYI</a></p>\n<p>&mdash; New Zealand Hong Konger 🇳🇿🇭🇰 (@NZHongKonger) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/NZHongKonger/status/1190510661983293440?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">November 2, 2019</a></p></blockquote>\n<p><script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script></p>\n<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-width=\"550\" data-dnt=\"true\">\n<p lang=\"zh\" dir=\"ltr\">因为并不违反当地法律</p>\n<p>&mdash; HumanRightsCat (@HumanRightsCat) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/HumanRightsCat/status/1190516875651776513?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">November 2, 2019</a></p></blockquote>\n<p><script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script></p>\n<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-width=\"550\" data-dnt=\"true\">\n<p lang=\"zh\" dir=\"ltr\">估计是大头兵来新西兰买奶粉，顺便跑人家街头踢正步散播红色病毒！<br />小粉红们见此，激动的像是打了鸡血，兴奋的嗷嗷直叫。</p>\n<p>这比加拿大跑车炸街爱国更恶劣，像是在宣誓赤纳粹对新西兰的主权！</p>\n<p>新西兰政府必须雷霆手段处理此事，否则颜面尽失。</p>\n<p>引自<a href=\"https://twitter.com/7opk8wu2GokafWl?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@7opk8wu2GokafWl</a> <br /> <a href=\"https://t.co/pA5mUFyFm5\">pic.twitter.com/pA5mUFyFm5</a></p>\n<p>&mdash; 新闻大吐槽😷 (@TuCaoFakeNews) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/TuCaoFakeNews/status/1190509799177220096?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">November 2, 2019</a></p></blockquote>\n<p><script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script></p>\n<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-width=\"550\" data-dnt=\"true\">\n<p lang=\"zh\" dir=\"ltr\">如果发生在中国，打其他国家旗帜，大张旗鼓搞政治活动，这些人就倒霉了，参照国庆期间台湾游客在中山陵，打出台湾青天白日满地红旗帜，不到一分钟就被保安和公安带走。</p>\n<p>只不过新西兰不像中国那么玻璃心，不觉得“颜面尽失”“丧权辱国”“辱新”。NZL有言论自由，这种集会示威也不违法，小粉红才敢这么干</p>\n<p>&mdash; HumanRightsCat (@HumanRightsCat) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/HumanRightsCat/status/1190516738602913797?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">November 2, 2019</a></p></blockquote>\n<p><script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script></p>\n<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-width=\"550\" data-dnt=\"true\">\n<p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">When New Zealand renamed to be New XI&#39;s land or New Zealand Special Administrative Region of the People&#39;s Republic of China<br />WHY NZ police did not stop this</p>\n<p>&mdash; Wanna Sleep (@Ks_me) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/Ks_me/status/1190563209385672704?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">November 2, 2019</a></p></blockquote>\n<p><script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script></p>\n<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-width=\"550\" data-dnt=\"true\">\n<p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">Imagine trying to do this with an American flag in Beijing <a href=\"https://t.co/R3awYBjwHp\">https://t.co/R3awYBjwHp</a></p>\n<p>&mdash; Matthew Brooker (@mbrookerhk) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/mbrookerhk/status/1190570991086235648?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">November 2, 2019</a></p></blockquote>\n<p><script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script></p>\n<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-width=\"550\" data-dnt=\"true\">\n<p lang=\"zh\" dir=\"ltr\">之前就说了，nz被渗透严重，并且因为工作的关系，大多接触国内来的小粉红，认识二十六个字母就出国了，英联邦国家都没有法律禁止宣传共产主义. 警察只能出现维护秩序，禁止演变成骚乱或者斗殴，他们没有权力驱逐他们，而移民局不审核价值观</p>\n<p>&mdash; 叫啥不吃饭 (@7opk8wu2GokafWl) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/7opk8wu2GokafWl/status/1190453844590776321?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">November 2, 2019</a></p></blockquote>\n<p><script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script></p>\n<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-width=\"550\" data-dnt=\"true\">\n<p lang=\"zh\" dir=\"ltr\">China&#39;s military appeared on the street of New Zealand, march and wave the Chinese flag.<br />中國軍人於紐西蘭街頭八面威風，現場中國人拍案叫絕👏<a href=\"https://t.co/Tyh61jgUBh\">https://t.co/Tyh61jgUBh</a><br />●來源：<a href=\"https://twitter.com/badiucao?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@Badiucao</a>、大西北圍村佬<a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/NewChinaland?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#NewChinaland</a> <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/%E7%B4%90%E8%A5%BF%E8%98%AD?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#紐西蘭</a> <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/%E6%96%B0%E8%A5%BF%E8%98%AD?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#新西蘭</a> <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/LIHKG?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#LIHKG</a> <a href=\"https://t.co/tX77ySVEwH\">pic.twitter.com/tX77ySVEwH</a></p>\n<p>&mdash; LIHKG 討論區 (@lihkg_forum) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/lihkg_forum/status/1190538975238209536?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">November 2, 2019</a></p></blockquote>\n<p><script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script></p>\n<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-width=\"550\" data-dnt=\"true\">\n<p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">today HongKong Tomorrow the world <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/antichinazi?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#antichinazi</a> <a href=\"https://t.co/L6g241cXuU\">pic.twitter.com/L6g241cXuU</a></p>\n<p>&mdash; muj (@muj0217) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/muj0217/status/1190544723154391040?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">November 2, 2019</a></p></blockquote>\n<p><script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n","author":1019,"ca